TITLE: Getting Signed URLs with getSignedURL Method
DESCRIPTION: Legacy method to retrieve signed URLs for private files through API requests. Supports custom expiration times and key types.
SOURCE: https://github.com/pingdotgg/uploadthing/blob/main/docs/src/app/(docs)/api-reference/ut-api/page.mdx#2025-04-13_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
